==English==
===Noun===
'''blind''' (''plural'' '''blinds''')

#A cloth covering that can be drawn down to cover a window.
#A covering for a window consisting of narrow wooden, metal or plastic slats that can be rotated simultaneously so as to block light or allow light to pass between them.

